column5: Well I got out today for a couple hours musky fishing I boated 2 had 6 other follow strike or lost. Hope you enjoy the video. Please let me know what you think of the music I am playing around and would like to know what you like to hear with the videos.
That's great thank you.  The music is good.  Maybe have a few a little more upbeat.
And the stills are great too.
Music and footage is great! Keep em coming!
Very cool thx for sharing! x2
Good video and great music Mike   nice Hooka music, with muskies PRICELESS
I like Mike!   Keeping that up and one of these days you are gonna get the vid of a muskie hoooking up on the 8 which would be cool to see.  Cheers, Ron...
Thanks guys Does anyone know where to get royalty free music? I have spent a lot of time trying to find good music.
Hero2 or 3?  If 2, what setting?  Oddly, I could be in the clearest water filming with the GoProH2 and find that it is often poor quality.  Good to see ya enjoying your season Mike.
Hero 3 for the hero 2 you need a flat lens for underwater shots
